main: ^<sp:50> <p:short> Umm, sir, or ma’am, actually I can’t really tell, but could you please help me out? I seem to have gotten myself lost, and to be honest, I have absolutely no idea where I am.
^<sp:50> Like, is this a beach or something? Or a desert? How did I get here? Where is here?
^<sp:25> It seems you have lost your memory of what you just went through. How unfortunate.
^<sp:50> Wh-what do you mean? Where am I??? Who are you???
^<sp:25> It isn’t my time to talk yet. You’ll have to regain your memories before coming back here.
^<sp:25> Regain your memories, and everything will make sense. E-Col will tell you what to do, just like before. Until then, I’ll be seeing you.
